Hi all,

Having issues with KSP. Particularly with going from my space station to the space centre. I have uploaded my logs to Dropbox and there is a link at the end of this post. I have the following mods:

KER
Mechjeb
SafeChute (doesn't work)
TweakScale
DMagic orbital science
Planetary base systems
KW Rocketry
ModuleAnitmateEmissive
Triggertech
SpaceY
SCANsat
Near future collection
Community Resource Pack
Interstellar fuel switch
KIS
KAS
FuelTanksPlus
Solaris Hypernautics

As far as I know the only things I use on my station is the nearfuture construction pack and MechJeb, Oh and KAS as I've strutted my station to make it more rigid. Perhaps it's time to backup my save and move to 1.0.5? Currently on 1.0.4.861

Any help you could provide would be good

Cheers All
